ame}</a> {/exp:channel:categories} <img src="../images/dotted-seperator.png" /><br />\n      <h2>News Archive</h2>\n      <img src="../images/dotted-seperator.png" /><br />\n      <h2>Newsletter Sign-Up</h2>\n      <p>To receive our Footnotes Newsletters please provide us with your email address:</p>\n      <form action="http://campaign.q-ux.com/t/r/s/tduypj/" method="post">\n        <p>\n          <label for="fieldEmail">Email</label>\n          <br />\n          <input id="fieldEmail" name="cm-tduypj-tduypj" type="email" required />\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          <button type="submit" class="wpsb_form_btn">Submit</button>\n        </p>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--wrapper--> \n\n{embed=''includes/footer''}'),
(15, 8, 'exp_templates', 'template_data', 1399380139, 1, '{embed=''includes/xhtml'' page_title="Login"}\n\n{embed=''includes/header''}\n\n\n<div class="wrapper">\n<div class="interior-content">\n        <div id="mainColumn" class="wide">\n							<h1>Login</h1>\n				<h2><a href="http://www.bidumbaugh.com/">Bid UMBAUGH</a></h2>\n<p>To better serve the needs of our clients issuing  bonds through a competitive bidding process, we have partnered with  Grant Street Group to offer electronic bidding services. Electronic  bidding provides our clients with better access to the municipal bond  market, creating interest from investment bankers from across the  nation. Access to the national bond markets frequently increases the  number bids received for bonds being issued competitively, and can  result in lower interest costs for the bonds.</p>\n<h2><a href="http://links.umbaugh.com/">Employee Portal</a></h2>\n<p>Umbaugh Employee Links. This site is restricted to Umbaugh employees.</p>\n								</div>\n        <div id="sideColumn">\n		<div id="nav_menu-2" class="widget widget_nav_menu"><div class="menu-sidebar-menu-container"><ul id="menu-sidebar-menu" class="menu"><li id="menu-item-255" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-255"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/about">More About Us</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-64" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-64"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/contact">Contact Us</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-65" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-65"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/join-our-firm">Join Our Firm</a></li>\n</ul></div></div>        </div>\n	</div>\n\n</div><!--wrapper-->\n\n\n\n{embed=''includes/footer''}\n'),
