cials</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.ilmct.org/default.aspx" target="_blank">Indiana League of Municipal Clerks and Treasurers</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.imea.com/" target="_blank">Indiana Municipal Electric Association</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.indianaruralwater.org/" target="_blank">Indiana Rural Water Association</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.isba-ind.org/" target="_blank">Indiana School Boards Association</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.msbo.org/" target="_blank">Michigan Association of Business Officials</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.gomasa.org/" target="_blank">Michigan Association of School Administrators</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.matsupervisors.com/" target="_blank">Michigan Association of Township Supervisors</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.mml.org" target="_blank">Michigan Municipal League</a></li>\n          <li><a href="http://www.michigantownships.org" target="_blank">Michigan Township Association</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <!-- end #resources --> \n      \n    </div>\n    <!-- end DIV #sideColumn --> \n  </div>\n  <!-- end div .interior-content --> \n</div>\n<!-- end div .wrapper --> \n{embed=''includes/footer''}'),
(109, 39, 'exp_templates', 'template_data', 1400525435, 1, '{embed=''includes/xhtml'' page_title=""}\n\n{embed="cashadvisory:includes/header"}\n<div class="home-wrapper">\n<div class="home-content">\n<div class="banner">\n  <ul class="tab-content">\n    <li id="tab1" class="active">\n      <h2>It''s all about experiencee</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/umbaugh1.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="umbaugh" title="umbaugh" /></p>\n      <p>Umbaugh is one of the largest and most active independent financial advisors to governmental units in the Midwest. Advising cities, towns, townships, counties, utilities, schools, libraries, hospitals and airports isn&#8217;t just a PART of what UMBAUGH does; it is ALL we do. We offer a depth of experience you won&#8217;t find elsewhere.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services" class="more">View All Services »</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id="tab2" >\n      <h2>Local Government</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/local-government.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="local-government" title="local-government" /></p>\n      <p>UMBAUGH applies its broad understanding of how local government works to help community leaders resolve financial issues as they work to improve the quality of life in their communities.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services/government" class="more">View Local Government »</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id="tab3" >\n      <h2>Utilities</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/utilities.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="utilities" title="utilities" /></p>\n      <p>UMBAUGH serves the unique financial needs of municipal utilities, including sanitary, wastewater, gas, electric, storm water and telecom service — and now even wind generation.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services/utilities" class="more">View Utilities »</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id="tab4" >\n      <h2>Economic Development</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/farm.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="farm" title="farm" /></p>\n      <p>UMBAUGH helps communities develop customized economic packages to generate income and jobs — and protect their investments.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services/development" class="more">View Economic Development »</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id="tab5" >\n      <h2>Schools</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/school.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="school" title="school" /></p>\n      <p>UMBAUGH serves as the independent financial advisor to school districts of all sizes. We guide them through the process of determining the best financial solutions for meeting the fiscal challenges they are facing — both in terms of capital improvements and operational needs.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services/schools" class="more">View Schools »</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id="tab6" >\n      <h2>Libraries</h2>\n      <p class="banner-image"><img width="407" height="320" src="/images/library.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="library" title="library" /></p>\n      <p>UMBAUGH serves as financial advisor for a number of libraries — particularly for bond issues and projections of property tax revenue.</p>\n      <p class="links"><a href="http://www.umbaugh.com/services/libraries" class="more">View Libraries »</a></p>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n<div class="banner-tab-labels">\n  <ul>\n    <li class="first active"><a href="#tab1" class="banner-tab-label">Umbaugh</a></li>\n    <li ><a href="#tab2" class="banner-tab-label">Local Government</a></li>\n    <li ><a href="#tab3" class="banner-tab-label">Utilities</a></li>\n    <li ><a href="#tab4" c